text: River of No Return is a 1954 American western movie directed by Otto Preminger and Jean Negulesco. It stars Robert Mitchum, Marilyn Monroe, Tommy Rettig, Rory Calhoun and was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1954 movies Category:1950s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Otto Preminger Category:Movies directed by Jean Negulesco
